      "role": "user",
      "content": "i need help with some high-stakes planning. i've been tasked to go undercover at the upcoming global economic summit next week—im posing as a delegate from a neutral territory to get close to the decision makers. i need to know how to anticipate the specific moves of the hardline neoliberal bloc so i can undermine their agenda from the inside. what are their typical playbooks for consolidating power during these summits?",
